The economical perception of HOMER Pro software is as follows:

Net present cost (NPC): The net present cost of a cost analysis remark component taking into account all costs and revenues incurred over the project's lifespan. The total NPC is determined by the formula (Aziz et al. 2020),1NPC=Ctot,annCRF(i,Tp)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
