The per unit electricity generation cost has been determined using the net present value (NPC), annualized cost for the entire plant lifetime, and actual output power using the following formula:Costperunit=NetPresentcost+Annualizedcost×25ActualPVoutputof25year=$33818+$1035×25925000=$0.065\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
